WEBVTT


00:00:00.360 --> 00:00:01.680
No goes

00:00:10.640 --> 00:00:12.562
animal abuse, 

00:00:12.562 --> 00:00:14.760
no animal abuse.

00:00:24.232 --> 00:00:26.138
Respect animals,

00:00:26.139 --> 00:00:28.888
please do not leave them tied to the sun, 

00:00:28.888 --> 00:00:29.739
to the water.

00:00:29.740 --> 00:00:32.670
Our animals feel the same way we do

00:00:32.671 --> 00:00:33.888
than our children,

00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:35.553
is sacrilege,

00:00:35.554 --> 00:00:37.421
it is a sin to mistreat them,

00:00:37.422 --> 00:00:39.361
then join us

00:00:39.362 --> 00:00:41.733
and be the voice of animals in their homes.

00:00:42.055 --> 00:00:44.324
Help respect our animals.

00:00:48.679 --> 00:00:50.900
We ask people who have their vehicle

00:00:50.959 --> 00:00:52.360
to be careful on the roads,

00:00:52.719 --> 00:00:55.159
they are totally innocent beings

00:00:55.160 --> 00:00:56.280
who do not know how to pass the street.

00:00:56.281 --> 00:00:57.400
We invite people

00:00:57.401 --> 00:00:58.821
and roadway drivers

00:00:59.039 --> 00:01:01.080
who have more responsibility in this regard.

00:01:01.279 --> 00:01:02.379
You see a little animal,

00:01:02.380 --> 00:01:05.241
please stop and allow him to pass on the road,

00:01:05.680 --> 00:01:07.968
we cannot continue to be in these situations

00:01:07.969 --> 00:01:10.251
where we are claiming a few women,

00:01:10.252 --> 00:01:10.981
some men

00:01:10.982 --> 00:01:12.245
that are accompanying us

00:01:12.351 --> 00:01:13.607
by the voice of the animals

00:01:13.608 --> 00:01:15.561
in this type of very delicate case

00:01:15.562 --> 00:01:18.311
and remember that you are not invisible beings,

00:01:18.312 --> 00:01:19.449
are part of us,

00:01:19.450 --> 00:01:20.647
are God's creation.

00:01:20.871 --> 00:01:22.928
We invite this community that today

00:01:23.240 --> 00:01:24.492
put a stop to your way

00:01:24.493 --> 00:01:26.323
and think more about these little animals

00:01:26.324 --> 00:01:27.371
that do us so much good.

00:01:27.372 --> 00:01:29.871
They change our lives and are beings of light.

00:01:34.112 --> 00:01:36.210
and the idea is to accompany these colleagues

00:01:36.211 --> 00:01:37.935
and call on the entire community to

00:01:37.936 --> 00:01:39.239
because it is a lack of awareness.

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:40.646
Drivers also

00:01:40.647 --> 00:01:42.164
to please respect the roads

00:01:42.392 --> 00:01:43.987
the life of animals
